{"tid":2113490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"領展關場消毒 店東轟港府不力","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T07:29:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb09ca8e3047f6ebc33cd948062f555f8695719","tid":2113490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/OOWTZCZB77P7SOBDVZP6A6J2AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2FOOWTZCZB77P7SOBDVZP6A6J2AM%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=ed230a47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2FOOWTZCZB77P7SOBDVZP6A6J2AM%2F&h=8746a104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/OOWTZCZB77P7SOBDVZP6A6J2AM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n領展關場消毒 店東轟港府不力<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】慈雲山連日來有多宗確診個案，管理慈雲山中心的領展宣佈商場及街市一連兩天關閉消毒，明日早上6時半重開。有街坊認為關閉商場及街市大清洗較令人安心，但在慈雲山經營餐廳的東主則狠批港府抗疫不力，才會屢屢影響民生。<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山商場及街市昨日起關閉兩天，本報記者昨午到場觀察，街市及商場範圍內所有商舖包括便利店、快餐店、手搖飲品店等全部「落閘」，門外貼上告示，通知街坊停業兩天。有麵包店職員關店前戴上口罩及面罩盤點貨品，並清洗麵包盤等用具。由於商戶仍可進出商場，商場各個出口均有保安為商戶量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MLmYYiTJxCtdR7vBrwa7Dc9zK9E=/1358x675/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4PZSKKM7XIA5HWNPZ4IV5PE72I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMLmYYiTJxCtdR7vBrwa7Dc9zK9E%3D%2F1358x675%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4PZSKKM7XIA5HWNPZ4IV5PE72I.gif&h=af6a9b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慈雲山街市檔口養了兩隻貓，義工擔心消毒劑影響其健康。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長者摸門釘 「麵包都冇得買」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賽馬會朗逸居院友 職員 染疫<br />\n<br />\n雖然多家店舖均貼出告示，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n居於慈正邨的唐小姐於毓華。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n於區內經營餐廳的Alex原本打算經商。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n隨商場及街市關閉大清洗，有。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f8c2195ad4683100037a6e186118fbf394a6a0f4","tid":2113490,"uid":33916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"個店東是咪已經犯左國安法"}]}